  <div class="comment_text">Exclusions are one thing, but I&#x27;ve had Backblaze _fail to restore a file_. I pay for unlimited history.<p>I contacted the support asking WTF, &quot;oh the file got deleted at some point, sorry for that&quot;, and they offered me 3 months of credits.<p>I do not trust my Backblaze backups anymore.</div>
