<div class="comment" id="comment-47763287">
  <div class="comment_head"><a href="/user/fuckinpuppers">fuckinpuppers</a> 1 day ago</div>
  <div class="comment_text">I noticed this (thankfully before it was critical) and I’ve decided to move on from BB. Easily over 10 year customer. Totally bogus. Not only did it stop backing it up the old history is totally gone as well.<p>The one thing they have to do is backup everything and when you see it in their console you can rest assured they are going to continue to back it up.<p>They’ve let the desktop client linger, it’s difficult to add meaningful exceptions. It’s obvious they want everyone to use B2 now.</div>
